subject: oem : Set the Core count property under CPU object
commitMessage:
oem : Set the Core count property under CPU object

- Parse the entity association map & based on the number
  of cores, set the corecount property under the CPU
  dbus object that is hosted by phosphor-invenory-manager

Signed-off-by: Manojkiran Eda <manojkiran.eda@gmail.com>
